name: Organization check
descriptionHtml:
### Endpoint for check organization is existed.

Request payload must contain the following fields:

organiazation_code: STRING

Request:

POST - https://apiqa.inquitech.in/api/v1/organizations/checkOrg

raw 
  {
    "organization_code": "rk223",
        "organization_name": "rk college"

}

200 - OK
